parameters:
Oh, are you looking for a part-time job? It's our busiest
time, so that's a big help! Well then, please start right
away.
Miss! I'd like to place an order!
Is the barley shuwa ready yet?
\c[31]Here you go, one ice-cold barley shuwa, coming up!
Oh, here it comes! The party's starting! Cheers!!
\c[31]Leave the poster girl duties to me!
Good job! Here's your pay for today!

Hey, missy. Weapons are useless unless you equip them. Order
the best one!
Then give me the best one there is!
This place is known for its exquisite monster cuisine.
Monster cuisine... It takes courage to eat it, doesn't it?
What kind of monster dish will be served?

The dessert of slime with kinako sprinkled on top comes
highly recommended.
Liquor! I can't help but drink!
Ohoo~, there there, good girl! You're as cute as I am!
What a predicament... what a predicament... *glances around*

What's wrong, miss? You're making it quite obvious that
you're in trouble.
Actually, some thugs stole my precious grimoire...
That's terrible, my condolences. Well then, goodbye!
Hey, Memerisu-chan! Let's help her out!!

Why do I have to retrieve a grimoire from thugs for some
lady I don't even know?!
That's what I wanted to hear. Leave it to me!
Wow, talk about a quick turnaround!?
You've accepted the quest to subdue the thugs!

The thugs are holed up in the ruins within the village, good
luck!

The thugs are holed up in the ruins within the village, so
take care!

Really!? I'm surprised you actually managed to get it
back...

There's no way I could lose! I want to know what defeat
feels like~!
...Indeed! This is the grimoire I asked for!

Now that we have our item back, it's time to collect the
promised goods, don't you think?

But... I didn't really think you'd get it back... I don't
have any money.
I'll give you this, so please forgive me☆
You've obtained the Rabbit Ear Ornament!

Huh? This isn't money!? Youuuuuuuu!!! I won't forgive
you!!!!

Hey, come on! It's not right to be after money in the first
place!
Waaaaahhhhh!!! I want a hundred trillion yen~~~~!!!
Thanks for getting the grimoire back for me♪
There's a lot of alcohol here since it's a tavern.
Eroge heroines are all over 18, so it's safe, safe!
Even so, you can't drink it!!!
There's plenty of alcohol since it's a tavern.
It's safe, safe! All eroge heroines are over 18!
Even so, you can't drink it!!!

Because it's a tavern, there's plenty of alcohol around,
huh.
Eroge heroines are all over 18, so it's safe, safe!
Even so, you mustn't drink it!!!
There's plenty of alcohol since it's a tavern.
All eroge heroines are over 18, so it's safe!
Even so, you can't drink it!!!
